snippet.title: Sketchbots Demo Trailer (OLD) | November 2020
snippet.description:
NOTE: This trailer doesn't show the current state of the game. The newest trailer can be found here: https://youtu.be/9-GE_-AOXso
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1456770/Sketchbots/

Program your robot and solve over 60 increasingly complex turn-based puzzles. Sharpen your skills, duel with friends, and create your own levels!

Song and game soundtrack by Luka Ilić

Find us on Discord: https://discord.com/invite/QdHxVCzuv5
Social: https://linktr.ee/feelgoodopg
